---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Uses | Joe Karlsson" description="Hardware, software, and gear I use daily for development, content creation, and my homelab.">
	<div class="mx-auto max-w-3xl px-4 py-8">
		<h1 class="mb-2 text-4xl font-bold md:text-5xl">
			<span class="text-coral">Uses</span>
		</h1>
		<p class="mb-2 text-lg text-gray-400">
			Hardware, software, and gear I use daily for development, content creation, and running my homelab.
		</p>
		<p class="mb-8 text-sm text-gray-500">Last updated: March 2026</p>

		<img
			src="/images/blog/how-i-work/IMG_2685.jpg"
			alt="Joe Karlsson's desk setup"
			class="mb-10 w-full rounded-lg border border-surface-3"
			loading="eager"
		/>

		<!-- ═══════════════════════════════════════════ -->
		<!-- 1. Desk & Hardware                         -->
		<!-- ═══════════════════════════════════════════ -->
		<section class="mb-12">
			<h2 class="mb-6 text-2xl font-bold text-teal">Desk & Hardware</h2>

			<p class="text-xs font-mono text-teal mb-3">computer & monitors</p>
			<div class="divide-y divide-surface-3/50">
				<div class="py-3">
					<p class="text-sm text-gray-300"><strong class="text-white">MacBook Pro M3 Pro</strong> &mdash; 36 GB RAM. A massive upgrade from the M1 Air &mdash; the extra cores and memory make a real difference for Docker, multiple IDEs, and running local AI models.</p>
				</div>
				<div class="py-3">
					<p class="text-sm text-gray-300"><strong class="text-white">Monitors</strong> &mdash; <a href="https://www.amazon.com/Lenovo-ThinkVision-P27h-10-LED-Monitor/dp/B071DK1TW8" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="text-coral hover:text-teal">ThinkVision P27h-10</a> 27" QHD (right) + <a href="https://www.amazon.com/Dell-U2723QE-UltraSharp-USB-C-Monitor/dp/B09TQZP9CL" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="text-coral hover:text-teal">Dell U3417W</a> 34" 4K (left). If I were buying today, I'd go ultrawide.</p>
				</div>
				<div class="py-3">
					<p class="text-sm text-gray-300"><strong class="text-white">Ergotron LX Dual Monitor Arm</strong> &mdash; lets me reposition monitors based on what I'm working on and frees up desk space for hardware projects.</p>
				</div>
				<div class="py-3">
					<p class="text-sm text-gray-300"><strong class="text-white"><a href="https://www.amazon.com/Dell-452-BCYT-D6000-Universal-Black/dp/B071YTQBXM" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="text-coral hover:text-teal">Dell Universal Dock D6000</a></strong> &mdash; bought used on eBay for under $100. Single USB-C cable for power, monitors, and all USB accessories.</p>
				</div>
			</div>

			<p class="text-xs font-mono text-teal mb-3 mt-6">input & peripherals</p>
			<div class="divide-y divide-surface-3/50">
				<div class="py-3">
					<p class="text-sm text-gray-300"><strong class="text-white">Razer DeathAdder Chroma</strong> &mdash; gaming mouse.</p>
				</div>
				<div class="py-3">
					<p class="text-sm text-gray-300"><strong class="text-white">Apple Magic Trackpad 2</strong> &mdash; for swipe and pinch controls.</p>
				</div>
				<div class="py-3">
					<p class="text-sm text-gray-300"><strong class="text-white">Razer Goliathus Extended Chroma</strong> &mdash; mousepad with RGB backlighting.</p>
				</div>
			</div>

			<p class="text-xs font-mono text-teal mb-3 mt-6">keyboards</p>
			<img
				src="/images/blog/how-i-work/5422ABA8-496F-41FD-83A0-E04FD7807046-1024x823.jpg"
				alt="Joe's mechanical keyboards"
				class="mb-4 w-full rounded-lg border border-surface-3"
				loading="lazy"
			/>
			<div class="divide-y divide-surface-3/50">
				<div class="py-3">
					<p class="text-sm text-gray-300"><strong class="text-white"><a href="https://www.amazon.com/gp/product/B072LZ2YRM" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="text-coral hover:text-teal">Vortexgear Race 3</a></strong> &mdash; with Cherry MX Clear switches.</p>
				</div>
				<div class="py-3">
					<p class="text-sm text-gray-300"><strong class="text-white">Custom Vortex POK3R</strong> &mdash; wood case, Cherry MX Blue switches, custom keycap set from WASD Keyboards. I like clicky switches &mdash; Blues are the loudest and clickiest. I'd recommend Clears as a good starter switch.</p>
				</div>
			</div>

			<p class="text-xs font-mono text-teal mb-3 mt-6">desk & audio</p>
			<div class="divide-y divide-surface-3/50">
				<div class="py-3">
					<p class="text-sm text-gray-300"><strong class="text-white">Standing Desk</strong> &mdash; custom-built IKEA desktop on industrial black steel legs, with a Luna Standing Desk Stool.</p>
				</div>
				<div class="py-3">
					<p class="text-sm text-gray-300"><strong class="text-white"><a href="https://www.amazon.com/Sony-MDR7506-Professional-Diaphragm-Headphone/dp/B000AJIF4E" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="text-coral hover:text-teal">Sony MDR7506</a></strong> &mdash; professional headphones with upgraded velvet pads. Affordable, comfortable, and sound great.</p>
				</div>
				<div class="py-3">
					<p class="text-sm text-gray-300"><strong class="text-white"><a href="https://www.bestbuy.com/site/philips-hue-play-white-color-ambiance-smart-led-bar-light-2-pack-multicolor/6298635.p" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="text-coral hover:text-teal">Philips Hue Play</a></strong> &mdash; White & Color Ambiance LED Bar Lights (2-Pack) for desk backlighting.</p>
				</div>
			</div>

			<div class="mt-6 grid grid-cols-2 gap-4">
				<img src="/images/blog/how-i-work/IMG_2687-1024x576.jpg" alt="Desk setup angle 1" class="rounded-lg border border-surface-3" loading="lazy" />
				<img src="/images/blog/how-i-work/IMG_2688-1024x576.jpg" alt="Desk setup angle 2" class="rounded-lg border border-surface-3" loading="lazy" />
			</div>
		</section>

		<!-- ═══════════════════════════════════════════ -->
		<!-- 2. Recording & Content                     -->
		<!-- ═══════════════════════════════════════════ -->
		<section class="mb-12">
			<h2 class="mb-6 text-2xl font-bold text-teal">Recording & Content</h2>

			<p class="text-xs font-mono text-teal mb-3">camera & audio</p>
			<div class="divide-y divide-surface-3/50">
				<div class="py-3">
					<p class="text-sm text-gray-300"><strong class="text-white"><a href="https://www.obsbot.com/obsbot-tiny-2" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="text-coral hover:text-teal">OBSBOT Tiny 2</a></strong> &mdash; 4K AI-powered webcam with gesture control and auto-tracking. Replaced my Sony A6600 &mdash; much simpler setup for Zoom calls and recordings.</p>
				</div>
				<div class="py-3">
					<p class="text-sm text-gray-300"><strong class="text-white"><a href="https://www.elgato.com/us/en/p/wave-3-black" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="text-coral hover:text-teal">Elgato Wave:3</a></strong> &mdash; USB condenser mic, managed through <a href="https://www.elgato.com/us/en/s/wave-link" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="text-coral hover:text-teal">Wave Link</a> for mixing. Replaced the Blue Yeti &mdash; much better sound and integrates with the Elgato ecosystem.</p>
				</div>
			</div>

			<p class="text-xs font-mono text-teal mb-3 mt-6">streaming & recording</p>
			<div class="divide-y divide-surface-3/50">
				<div class="py-3">
					<p class="text-sm text-gray-300"><strong class="text-white"><a href="https://www.elgato.com/en/gaming/stream-deck" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="text-coral hover:text-teal">Elgato Stream Deck</a></strong> &mdash; controlling streams and shortcuts.</p>
				</div>
				<div class="py-3">
					<p class="text-sm text-gray-300"><strong class="text-white"><a href="https://obsproject.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="text-coral hover:text-teal">OBS</a></strong> &mdash; Open Broadcaster Software for streaming.</p>
				</div>
				<div class="py-3">
					<p class="text-sm text-gray-300"><strong class="text-white"><a href="https://www.techsmith.com/camtasia.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="text-coral hover:text-teal">Camtasia</a></strong> &mdash; video editing for tutorials and demos.</p>
				</div>
				<div class="py-3">
					<p class="text-sm text-gray-300"><strong class="text-white"><a href="https://www.screen.studio/" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="text-coral hover:text-teal">Screen Studio</a></strong> &mdash; polished screen recordings with auto-zoom.</p>
				</div>
				<div class="py-3">
					<p class="text-sm text-gray-300"><strong class="text-white"><a href="https://xnipapp.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="text-coral hover:text-teal">Xnip</a></strong> &mdash; screenshot tool with annotations and scrolling capture.</p>
				</div>
			</div>

			<p class="text-xs font-mono text-teal mb-3 mt-6">lighting & green screen</p>
			<div class="divide-y divide-surface-3/50">
				<div class="py-3">
					<p class="text-sm text-gray-300"><strong class="text-white"><a href="https://www.amazon.com/gp/product/B07L755X9G" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="text-coral hover:text-teal">Elgato Key Lights</a> (x2)</strong> &mdash; plus professional studio LED panels.</p>
				</div>
				<div class="py-3">
					<p class="text-sm text-gray-300"><strong class="text-white"><a href="https://www.amazon.com/gp/product/B00JSAOGWG" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="text-coral hover:text-teal">Fancierstudio Collapsible Green/Blue Screen</a></strong> &mdash; on a <a href="https://www.amazon.com/gp/product/B00PLEX7Q4" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="text-coral hover:text-teal">Fovitec 7'6" Clip Stand</a>.</p>
				</div>
			</div>
		</section>

		<!-- ═══════════════════════════════════════════ -->
		<!-- 3. Dev Tools & Software                    -->
		<!-- ═══════════════════════════════════════════ -->
		<section class="mb-12">
			<h2 class="mb-6 text-2xl font-bold text-teal">Dev Tools & Software</h2>

			<p class="text-xs font-mono text-teal mb-3">editors</p>
			<div class="divide-y divide-surface-3/50">
				<div class="py-3">
					<p class="text-sm text-gray-300"><strong class="text-white"><a href="https://code.visualstudio.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="text-coral hover:text-teal">Visual Studio Code</a></strong> &mdash; still my primary editor. Monokai theme + <a href="https://marketplace.visualstudio.com/items?itemName=vscode-icons-team.vscode-icons" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="text-coral hover:text-teal">vscode-icons</a>.</p>
				</div>
				<div class="py-3">
					<p class="text-sm text-gray-300"><strong class="text-white"><a href="https://www.cursor.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="text-coral hover:text-teal">Cursor</a></strong> &mdash; AI-powered fork of VS Code, increasingly my go-to for new projects.</p>
				</div>
				<div class="py-3">
					<p class="text-sm text-gray-300"><strong class="text-white">Key extensions</strong> &mdash; <a href="https://marketplace.visualstudio.com/items?itemName=eamodio.gitlens" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="text-coral hover:text-teal">GitLens</a>, <a href="https://marketplace.visualstudio.com/items?itemName=esbenp.prettier-vscode" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="text-coral hover:text-teal">Prettier</a> + <a href="https://marketplace.visualstudio.com/items?itemName=dbaeumer.vscode-eslint" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="text-coral hover:text-teal">ESLint</a>, <a href="https://marketplace.visualstudio.com/items?itemName=github.copilot-chat" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="text-coral hover:text-teal">GitHub Copilot</a>, Docker, Remote SSH, Go/Python/Svelte support.</p>
				</div>
			</div>

			<p class="text-xs font-mono text-teal mb-3 mt-6">ai tools</p>
			<div class="divide-y divide-surface-3/50">
				<div class="py-3">
					<p class="text-sm text-gray-300"><strong class="text-white"><a href="https://docs.anthropic.com/en/docs/claude-code" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="text-coral hover:text-teal">Claude Code</a> (CLI)</strong> &mdash; my primary coding companion. I use it in the terminal for everything from infrastructure automation to building this website. It manages my homelab, writes deployment scripts, and helps debug across 40+ containers.</p>
				</div>
				<div class="py-3">
					<p class="text-sm text-gray-300"><strong class="text-white"><a href="https://claude.ai/download" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="text-coral hover:text-teal">Claude</a> desktop app</strong> &mdash; writing, research, and brainstorming.</p>
				</div>
				<div class="py-3">
					<p class="text-sm text-gray-300"><strong class="text-white"><a href="https://github.com/features/copilot" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="text-coral hover:text-teal">GitHub Copilot</a></strong> &mdash; inline code completion in VS Code and Cursor.</p>
				</div>
				<div class="py-3">
					<p class="text-sm text-gray-300"><strong class="text-white"><a href="https://superwhisper.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="text-coral hover:text-teal">superwhisper</a></strong> &mdash; local speech-to-text, great for dictating docs and messages.</p>
				</div>
				<div class="py-3">
					<p class="text-sm text-gray-300"><strong class="text-white"><a href="https://wakatime.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="text-coral hover:text-teal">WakaTime</a></strong> &mdash; like a Fitbit for programmers, automated time tracking and metrics.</p>
				</div>
			</div>

			<p class="text-xs font-mono text-teal mb-3 mt-6">terminal</p>
			<div class="divide-y divide-surface-3/50">
				<div class="py-3">
					<p class="text-sm text-gray-300"><strong class="text-white"><a href="https://iterm2.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="text-coral hover:text-teal">iTerm2</a></strong> &mdash; with <a href="https://ohmyz.sh/" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="text-coral hover:text-teal">Oh My Zsh</a> and <a href="https://github.com/romkatv/powerlevel10k" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="text-coral hover:text-teal">Powerlevel10k</a> theme. Plugins: git, z, zsh-autosuggestions, zsh-syntax-highlighting.</p>
				</div>
				<div class="py-3">
					<p class="text-sm text-gray-300"><strong class="text-white">Dotfiles</strong> &mdash; config files at my <a href="https://github.com/JoeKarlsson/dotfiles" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="text-coral hover:text-teal">dotfiles repo</a> on GitHub.</p>
				</div>
			</div>

			<p class="text-xs font-mono text-teal mb-3 mt-6">productivity</p>
			<div class="divide-y divide-surface-3/50">
				<div class="py-3">
					<p class="text-sm text-gray-300"><strong class="text-white"><a href="https://www.raycast.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="text-coral hover:text-teal">Raycast</a></strong> &mdash; launcher, snippets, clipboard history.</p>
				</div>
				<div class="py-3">
					<p class="text-sm text-gray-300"><strong class="text-white"><a href="https://apps.apple.com/us/app/magnet/id441258766?mt=12" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="text-coral hover:text-teal">Magnet</a></strong> &mdash; window management.</p>
				</div>
				<div class="py-3">
					<p class="text-sm text-gray-300"><strong class="text-white"><a href="https://www.notion.so/" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="text-coral hover:text-teal">Notion</a></strong> &mdash; notes and docs.</p>
				</div>
				<div class="py-3">
					<p class="text-sm text-gray-300"><strong class="text-white"><a href="https://linear.app/" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="text-coral hover:text-teal">Linear</a></strong> &mdash; issue tracking.</p>
				</div>
				<div class="py-3">
					<p class="text-sm text-gray-300"><strong class="text-white"><a href="https://grammarly.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="text-coral hover:text-teal">Grammarly</a></strong> &mdash; writing assistant.</p>
				</div>
			</div>

			<p class="text-xs font-mono text-teal mb-3 mt-6">communication & media</p>
			<div class="divide-y divide-surface-3/50">
				<div class="py-3">
					<p class="text-sm text-gray-300"><strong class="text-white"><a href="https://rambox.pro/" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="text-coral hover:text-teal">Rambox</a></strong> &mdash; all messaging clients in one app.</p>
				</div>
				<div class="py-3">
					<p class="text-sm text-gray-300"><strong class="text-white"><a href="https://github.com/gitroomhq/postiz-app" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="text-coral hover:text-teal">Postiz</a></strong> &mdash; self-hosted social media scheduling (replaced Buffer).</p>
				</div>
				<div class="py-3">
					<p class="text-sm text-gray-300"><strong class="text-white"><a href="https://www.plex.tv/" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="text-coral hover:text-teal">Plex</a></strong> &mdash; self-hosted media streaming. <strong class="text-white"><a href="https://www.videolan.org/vlc/" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="text-coral hover:text-teal">VLC</a></strong> for everything else.</p>
				</div>
			</div>

			<p class="text-xs font-mono text-teal mb-3 mt-6">security & utilities</p>
			<div class="divide-y divide-surface-3/50">
				<div class="py-3">
					<p class="text-sm text-gray-300"><strong class="text-white"><a href="https://1password.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="text-coral hover:text-teal">1Password</a></strong> &mdash; password manager (+ self-hosted <a href="https://github.com/dani-garcia/vaultwarden" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="text-coral hover:text-teal">Vaultwarden</a> as backup).</p>
				</div>
				<div class="py-3">
					<p class="text-sm text-gray-300"><strong class="text-white"><a href="https://tailscale.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="text-coral hover:text-teal">Tailscale</a></strong> &mdash; mesh VPN for accessing homelab remotely.</p>
				</div>
				<div class="py-3">
					<p class="text-sm text-gray-300"><strong class="text-white"><a href="https://www.privateinternetaccess.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="text-coral hover:text-teal">Private Internet Access</a></strong> &mdash; commercial VPN for privacy on public networks.</p>
				</div>
				<div class="py-3">
					<p class="text-sm text-gray-300"><strong class="text-white"><a href="https://www.docker.com/products/docker-desktop/" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="text-coral hover:text-teal">Docker Desktop</a></strong> &mdash; <strong class="text-white"><a href="https://github.com/dwarvesf/hidden" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="text-coral hover:text-teal">Hidden Bar</a></strong> &mdash; <strong class="text-white"><a href="https://rogueamoeba.com/soundsource/" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="text-coral hover:text-teal">SoundSource</a></strong> (per-app audio control).</p>
				</div>
			</div>
		</section>

		<!-- ═══════════════════════════════════════════ -->
		<!-- 4. Homelab                                 -->
		<!-- ═══════════════════════════════════════════ -->
		<section class="mb-12">
			<h2 class="mb-4 text-2xl font-bold text-teal">Homelab</h2>
			<p class="mb-4 text-sm text-gray-400">
				I run a self-hosted <a href="https://www.proxmox.com/en/proxmox-virtual-environment" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="text-coral hover:text-teal">Proxmox VE</a> cluster with 40+ LXC containers and VMs across two rack-mounted servers. Everything from media automation to home security to document management runs locally on my own hardware.
			</p>
			<div class="space-y-3">
				<!-- Server Hardware -->
				<div class="rounded-lg border border-surface-3 bg-surface-1 p-5">
					<h3 class="mb-2 font-semibold text-white">Server Hardware</h3>
					<div class="space-y-4">
						<div>
							<p class="text-sm font-medium text-gray-300">prxbox1 &mdash; <a href="https://www.dell.com/support/kbdoc/en-us/000124164/dell-poweredge-r730-and-r730xd-system-guide" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="text-coral hover:text-teal">Dell PowerEdge R730</a></p>
							<ul class="mt-1 list-disc space-y-1 pl-5 text-sm text-gray-400">
								<li>2x Intel Xeon E5-2698 v4 @ 2.20 GHz (80 cores total)</li>
								<li>128 GB DDR4 ECC RAM</li>
								<li><a href="https://www.nvidia.com/en-us/design-visualization/quadro/rtx-4000/" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="text-coral hover:text-teal">NVIDIA Quadro RTX 4000</a> (8 GB VRAM)</li>
								<li>446 GB SSD (system) + 4.9 TB HDD + NAS mounts</li>
								<li>Dual <a href="https://www.intel.com/content/www/us/en/products/sku/82599/intel-ethernet-converged-network-adapter-x710da2/specifications.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="text-coral hover:text-teal">Intel X710</a> 10 Gb SFP+ in LACP bond (20 Gbps)</li>
								<li>Runs 26 containers/VMs &mdash; media automation, infrastructure, monitoring, home automation</li>
							</ul>
						</div>
						<div>
							<p class="text-sm font-medium text-gray-300">prxbox2 &mdash; <a href="https://www.dell.com/support/kbdoc/en-us/000124164/dell-poweredge-r730-and-r730xd-system-guide" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="text-coral hover:text-teal">Dell PowerEdge R730</a></p>
							<ul class="mt-1 list-disc space-y-1 pl-5 text-sm text-gray-400">
								<li><a href="https://www.nvidia.com/en-us/design-visualization/rtx-a4000/" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="text-coral hover:text-teal">NVIDIA RTX A4000</a> (16 GB VRAM)</li>
								<li>Dual <a href="https://www.intel.com/content/www/us/en/products/sku/82599/intel-ethernet-converged-network-adapter-x710da2/specifications.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="text-coral hover:text-teal">Intel X710</a> 10 Gb SFP+ in LACP bond (20 Gbps)</li>
								<li>Runs 15 containers &mdash; GPU-accelerated media playback, photo management, transcoding</li>
							</ul>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>

				<!-- GPUs -->
				<div class="rounded-lg border border-surface-3 bg-surface-1 p-5">
					<h3 class="mb-1 font-semibold text-white">GPU Workloads</h3>
					<ul class="mt-2 list-disc space-y-1 pl-5 text-sm text-gray-400">
